@Node Warning "Device Handler - WARNING"
@next Features
@prev Main

  @{b}This software is intended for advanced users only. I @{u}strongly@{uu}
  recommend all people who do not understand every detail given herein
  to obtain further information about AmigaDOS-Devices, Handlers and
  their implementation on top of Exec device drivers.

  @{fg highlight}
             WRONG USAGE OF THIS SOFTWARE WILL MOST LIKELY
                   RESULT IN SEVERE LOSS OF DATA!
